data.description: Check out this beautiful home in an amazing location just minutes from US 65 Highway and a short drive to multiple parks for the kids to run, play, and stretch their legs. With three bedrooms on the main level, two on the lower level, three full baths, two living spaces, there's room for everyone. Those who love to cook will appreciate the large pantry in this home, as well as the extra seating at the peninsula and stainless steel appliances. The walkout basement leads out to a good size backyard for kids to play and/or entertaining guests. When the home was being built, the owner spared no expense with the upgrades they selected to make this home theirs.The great neighborhood offers walking paths, a playground, and a swimming pool.
